(September 26, 1968)

(Republished)

Theodore S. Williams, Appellant, v. Sara Williams, Respondent.

Appeal from order entered April 10, 1968, unanimously dismissed, without costs and without disbursements. The order appealed from is not appealable as of right. The order of this court entered on September 19, 1968 [30 A D 2d 920] is vacated. Concur — Botein, P. J., Stevens, Eager, Tilzer and Rabin, JJ.
